{"tid":1802290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會久唔久懷疑下人生","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T22:44:41.000Z","uid":137043,"like":141,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7022eee1b20f1c817ed2dc0833a0b7f11b6a13e3","tid":1802290,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"突然會諗下點解我會存在、點解我會做緊手頭上呢樣野<br />\n又或者望望下啲相諗下點解以前同依家分別咁大<br />\n點解我會鐘意另一半、其實我喺度有咩意思<br />\n即時變左問題兒童，有十萬個為什麼<br />\n有時諗諗下會心情仲會變差<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無方法可以改善呢個情況？<br />\n同埋點解會有咁嘅事發生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8308ccf3321bd0ab0417cfe554b637fc69f75f2c","tid":1802290,"uid":50744,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:13:20.000Z","msg":"日日諗<br />\n而家癲9左"},{"pid":"239bf6a5c2077f22eeb9791b95201f274891f4c8","tid":1802290,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8308ccf3321bd0ab0417cfe554b637fc69f75f2c","tid":1802290,"uid":50744,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:13:20.000Z","msg":"日日諗<br />\n而家癲9左"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:16:48.000Z","msg":"有無成功諗到其中一條問題嘅答案"},{"pid":"ced7e4174f012270ce5e67cf08d057c8688f471c","tid":1802290,"uid":318284,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"我都諗唔通<br />\n經常頹<br />\n個陣就由自己頹<br />\n心情好返啲就慢慢將思考提升返現實小小嘅層次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>所以究竟有冇神/造物主？？</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df194c5eb0ea44c6006066f233325b0d2ecfdad4","tid":1802290,"uid":318284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:20:46.000Z","msg":"懷疑人生好正常嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884d1c50878a658290f6729eed8fe875ca22b628","tid":1802290,"uid":288086,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"我都成日諗人生<br />\n加埋睇書睇其他人嘅人生<br />\n係領悟咗好多野<br />\n但仍然覺得人生其實係好無謂好辛苦"},{"pid":"6c489145175c3cc3f481b54271016db1af9898dc","tid":1802290,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ced7e4174f012270ce5e67cf08d057c8688f471c","tid":1802290,"uid":318284,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"我都諗唔通<br />\n經常頹<br />\n個陣就由自己頹<br />\n心情好返啲就慢慢將思考提升返現實小小嘅層次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>所以究竟有冇神/造物主？？</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"之前讀過科關於science同religion，有提到究竟有無造物主呢樣野。然後個答案係睇你信科學定宗教多啲，無標準答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頹嗰陣會唔會做啲咩嘗試令自己快啲心情好啲？"},{"pid":"2a8ea29016c7c6928edc4e59037a51187b6adda2","tid":1802290,"uid":137043,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"884d1c50878a658290f6729eed8fe875ca22b628","tid":1802290,"uid":288086,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"我都成日諗人生<br />\n加埋睇書睇其他人嘅人生<br />\n係領悟咗好多野<br />\n但仍然覺得人生其實係好無謂好辛苦"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"Agger人生好無謂<br />\n生岀黎就係等老然後死咁<br />\n有人講過人生意義就係尋找意義嘅過程<br />\n但我又覺得用幾十年去搵個答案好浪費時間咁<br />\n同埋個人主張見步行步<br />\n成日見其他人一早plan定好耐之後嘅事<br />\n就覺得可能聽日就死，咁早諗定有咩用？<br />\n但唔plan又唔得，條路會辛苦啲"},{"pid":"03ffbc69a30d3e640091a2acb7876c9e273b97fd","tid":1802290,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"884d1c50878a658290f6729eed8fe875ca22b628","tid":1802290,"uid":288086,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyT